00:21:35,397 --> 00:21:37,174
- Anything else?
- Other than "no", no.

362
00:21:37,706 --> 00:21:40,466
Nicole, Luke. Nicole was here.

363
00:21:40,542 --> 00:21:44,993
She's the one who told you that I was here and didn't stay. She's new. Nothing new.

