00:21:45,089 --> 00:21:47,060
Well, you saw her, so it's not new.

365
00:21:47,251 --> 00:21:50,307
Oh, it's so new. What's going on there?

366
00:21:50,431 --> 00:21:54,869
- We're kind of seeing each other again.
